name: DOGUE
description: DOGUE – The Gentleman of Memecoins DOGUE is a memecoin born from the #DOGUE trend launched by Vogue. Our community loves to create stylish dogs to parody crypto and financial news through elegance and humor. Our mascot: a dogue in a suit and Prada glasses. He symbolizes today’s society, where many strive to show the most beautiful, the most chic—often just to get noticed. But very few embody the true gentleman. DOGUE, however, is that true Gentleman. Neither rich nor poor: he represents an alternative to the degeneracy omnipresent in the crypto world. We stand for elegance, beauty, and style—without pretension. DOGUE is the meeting point of memes, fashion, and timeless class.
